description:
These are the celebs you forgot were on American Horror Story. We’ll be looking at recognizable celebrities who appeared in American Horror Story, whether in a minor or starring role, but who, for a variety of reasons, you may not remember. Be prepared to say, “Oh yeah, they were in this.” WatchMojo ranks the celebs you forgot were on AHS. Are there any celebrities we forgot about? Let us know in the comments!
